{"tid":419474,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[智障樓主]有個關於機率嘅問題唔清楚想問下大家","createTime":"2017-09-30T13:49:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-30T14:38:37.000Z","uid":76399,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b5b9f62616f764f2f8eb1e7195f0e3be5417089c","tid":419474,"uid":76399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T13:49:57.000Z","msg":"戴返個頭盔先，我真係智障架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，大家屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n問題係咁嘅：依家有一個抽獎活動，為期九日，參加者要係三張牌抽一張卡。其中有一張係有獎品嘅，另外兩張就係乜都冇。 換言之每次中獎嘅機率就係三份一啦。<br />\n<br />\n假設依家有兩個參加者，A&amp;B<br />\n三張牌可稱為：1,2,3<br />\n而有獎品嘅牌每日都係隨機(可以係九日都係1號牌/可以九日都唔同[總之就係隨機])<br />\n<br />\n參加者A：每一次抽牌嘅時候都係會揀1號牌，啫係佢會揀9次1號牌<br />\n<br />\n參加者B：每一次抽牌嘅時候都係靠直覺，每次都係三份一機率抽一張隨機嘅牌<br />\n<br />\n理論上，參加者A每次都係揀1號牌，而抽獎次數為九次，啫係理論上佢九次抽獎內至少會中獎三次，Right？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果咁樣嘅話，到底參加者A中獎嘅機率大啲定係參加者B機率大啲？"},{"pid":"b722bf5ce4b38c04424d237af0be820ab7175f00","tid":419474,"uid":76399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T13:58:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d330ea9813d874d76dc4d18e56182739fcd02645","tid":419474,"uid":76399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T14:03:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7086ad95a18bad17dd18ed8fb63681d2f18d14dc","tid":419474,"uid":4536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T14:04:25.000Z","msg":"每次抽都係獨立事件，唔可以加埋一齊話最少中3次"},{"pid":"90233c3ea7f19870a83fc891664e6d3256f3e823","tid":419474,"uid":107945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T14:07:51.000Z","msg":"理論值應該係一樣<br />\nA係揀死一號，但有獎嘅牌係random，所以1/3<br />\nB求其揀，random揀再random牌，都係1/3<br />\n除非仼何一張牌有其他因素導致中獎機率大d，如果唔係都一樣"},{"pid":"3c2b16447eb252b51b995351353e7f887d9aec4f","tid":419474,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T14:10:17.000Z","msg":"一樣"},{"pid":"f158b1ee32f944642f664ce1ec0ce1588d821ec3","tid":419474,"uid":76399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T14:12:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每次抽都係獨立事件，唔可以加埋一齊話最少中3次</blockquote><br />\n但三份一嘅理論上嘅定義係每抽三次就有一次機會中嘛"},{"pid":"f85b91ba818f7168401a793e9a52bdf05688fca5","tid":419474,"uid":34929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T14:15:31.000Z","msg":"independent events: <br />\nP(B wins) = P(B wins | choose 1  )P(choose 1) + P(B wins | choose 2  )P(choose 2) + P(B wins | choose 3  )P(choose 3) = 1/3"},{"pid":"fae149d8a493cc09f4a631b56783bc819a071572","tid":419474,"uid":69522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T14:31:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每次抽都係獨立事件，唔可以加埋一齊話最少中3次</blockquote><br />\n油b絲打講出重點，每次都係獨立事件<br />\na第一回合抽到獎機會：1/3<br />\na第二回合抽到獎機會：1/3<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;<br />\nb第一回合抽到獎機會：1/3<br />\nb第二回合抽到獎機會：1/3<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n因為抽獎係獨立事件，所以上局抽獎唔會影響下一局結果。<br />\n<br />\n所以a同b無論係抽1次，9次 ，n次，得獎機會都一樣"},{"pid":"53963ee9ad28748e09fa47324b5cd54770d9f6ce","tid":419474,"uid":60464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T14:35:55.000Z","msg":"呢個case類似我以前mc卷唔識做走去撞<br />\n到底憑直覺撞會啱多啲定揀晒b會啱多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過根據多年經驗，撞晒同一個答案係啱多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f527ab9904f4817ff3c9ee44823f82627130c6f","tid":419474,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T14:37:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個case類似我以前mc卷唔識做走去撞<br />\n到底憑直覺撞會啱多啲定揀晒b會啱多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過根據多年經驗，撞晒同一個答案係啱多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你直覺影響左，唔係真係亂撞"},{"pid":"8731e31a77504a2dac425d80a78bbcdeaa7c5e13","tid":419474,"uid":76399,"like":0,"dislike":